title: From Vanity To Insanity - Onision's Story (James Jackson?)

media:group.media:title: From Vanity To Insanity - Onision's Story (James Jackson?)
media:group.media:description:
Currently Deemed "The Most Hated Youtuber", Onision's life and overall history warrants the title. His many actions almost seeming calculated, done in an overall effort to gain popularity through infamy.  He has been successful at that, stirring up an unfathomable amount of drama, with this video attempting to cover most of it.
